data.description: Welcome Home ! This 3 bedroom 1 bath Ranch flows with natural light throughout with hardwood floors in each room. Immense Family room located off of the back of the home for all your entertaining needs. Open layout Kitchen with wood cabinetry and enough room for a large island or current dining table arrangement. Bonus Living/Sitting room in the front of the home. Attached 1 car garage off of the enclosed hallway/entry way.
